commitResults.messageTitle: Add Increment : Level-0 Greet
Add Level-1 Echo, Exit
commitResults.messageBody:
Echo: Duke echoes any input given
Exit: Duke exits when input is "bye"

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Level-2 Add, List, Task Class
commitResults.messageBody:
Add: Inputs will add a Task to a fixed size array
List: Lists Tasks in input order
Task class: Contains string description of task

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Level-3 Done Update Task class, List
commitResults.messageBody:
Done: Mark tasks as done with input : "done 'task number' ".
Task class: Contains status of task (done/not done).
List: Shows status of task.

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix coding standard and tidying of code
Add ToDo, Deadline, Event
commitResults.messageBody:
ToDo, Deadline, and Event are subclasses of Task.
Add invalidInput to prevent invalid inputs from crashing program. Applies to Deadline and Event.
Add listTask() method to Task for better listing of task (printList()).
